&lt;li data-start=&quot;1762&quot; data-end=&quot;1839&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1764&quot; data-end=&quot;1839&quot;&gt;Inspect incoming vehicles for damage, cleanliness, and mechanical issues.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1840&quot; data-end=&quot;1918&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1842&quot; data-end=&quot;1918&quot;&gt;Identify and report problems that fall outside Clutch’s quality standards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1919&quot; data-end=&quot;1988&quot;&gt;
