&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;License:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Valid driver’s license (minimum G2)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work Authorization:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Legally authorized to work in Canada&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Ability to commute to Mississauga&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Availability:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Able to commit to a full-time schedule of 40 hours per week, including overtime based on business needs&lt;/p&gt;
