&lt;p data-start=&quot;492&quot; data-end=&quot;750&quot;&gt;Named two years in a row to the Globe &amp;amp; Mail’s list of the Top Growing Companies in Canada and also awarded spots on Deloitte’s Technology Fast 50™ and Fast 500™ lists, we’re looking to add curious, hard-working, and driven individuals to our growing team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;752&quot; data-end=&quot;1070&quot;&gt;Headquartered in Toronto, Clutch was founded in 2017 and currently services Ontario, New Brunswick, Nova Scotia, British Columbia, and Prince Edward Island. Clutch is backed by a number of world-class investors, including D1 Capital, Canaan, Real Ventures, Brand Project, and Upper90. To learn more, visit clutch.ca.&lt;/p&gt;
