&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Condition Report Writer&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;will oversee the coordination and optimization of inventory capture across multiple storage and facility locations. This role is responsible for ensuring accurate inventory records capturing, declarations and effective collaboration across departments. The ideal candidate will be highly organized, data-driven, and an eye for detail.&lt;/p&gt;
