&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Funding &amp;amp; Capital Partnerships (Warehouse / Forward Flow)&lt;/strong&gt;: Build and manage relationships with banks, credit funds, and capital partners. Lead diligence and lender reporting, negotiate facility terms (advance rates, eligibil

